OL,6,GStaff at the Peterborough-based
OL,7,Gteleshopping channel were called to a
OL,8,Gmeeting this morning to learn the
OL,9,Gfate of Ideal World after days of
OL,10,Gnegotiations with potential buyers.
OL,12,FAt the meeting it was confirmed that
OL,13,Fthe 250 staff working at Ideal World
OL,14,Fwill be made redundant after a buyer
OL,15,Ffailed to materialise.
OL,17,FThe channel was put up for sale last
OL,18,Fmonth as debts mounted. As suppliers
OL,19,Fpulled the plug on the channel, the
OL,20,Fchannel was forced to cease trading.
OL,3,CIdeal World fails to find a buyer `
OL,4,Cchannel doomed as staff made redundant
