OL,6,FIdeal World dropped off air at 3pm on
OL,7,FMonday afternoon, in what now appears
OL,8,Fto be the end of a tumultuous 18
OL,9,Fmonths for the company.
OL,11,FFormer owner Aurelius asset-stripped
OL,12,Fand sold off the remnants of Ideal
OL,13,FWorld in early 2022, in a move that
OL,14,Fsaw sister channel Create & Craft
OL,15,Fbeing sold to Hochanda and Ideal
OL,16,FWorld's original Freeview channel
OL,17,Fnumber traded with TJC for #7 million.
