OL,6,FIdeal Shopping Direct Limited was
OL,7,Fliquidated; the remaining business
OL,8,Ftransferred to a new company, Ideal
OL,9,FWorld Limited, under the control of
OL,10,Fnew owner and investor, Hamish
OL,11,FMorjaria.
OL,13,FUnder new ownership, the channel
OL,14,Ffocused on big brands, but despite a
OL,15,Flucrative deal with ITV giving the
OL,16,Fchannel overnight airtime on ITV 1
OL,17,Fand ITV 4, the business failed as
OL,18,Fdebts mounted up and suppliers ceased
OL,19,Fdoing business with the company.
