OL,6,FLast month, Financial and Risk
OL,7,FAdvisory company Kroll was appointed
OL,8,Fto seek a buyer for the company.
OL,9,FDespite management indicating there
OL,10,Fhad been interest, no firm offers
OL,11,Fmaterialised.
OL,13,FIn the meantime, Ideal World lost its
OL,14,Fslot on Sky's Electronic Programme
OL,15,FGuide after ceasing broadcasting.
OL,16,FSky's strict channel listing rules
OL,17,Fmean that broadcasters that are
OL,18,Funable to broadcast face the brisk
OL,19,Fremoval of their channel listing.
